{
  "url": "https://www.hymnal.net/cn/hymn/ts/439",
  "title": "神的大爱将我围困",
  "verses": [
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "D",
              "text": "神 阿，"
            },
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "你 的 大"
            },
            {
              "chord": "A",
              "text": "愛 將"
            },
            {
              "chord": "A7",
              "text": "我 圍"
            },
            {
              "chord": "D",
              "text": "困，"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "有 如 強 潮 澎"
            },
            {
              "chord": "E7",
              "text": "湃 迫"
            },
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "我 而"
            },
            {
              "chord": "A",
              "text": "來；"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "D",
              "text": "不 再"
            },
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "自 縛， 全"
            },
            {
              "chord": "G",
              "text": "人 歡"
            },
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "然 投"
            },
            {
              "chord": "D",
              "text": "順，"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "G",
              "text": "好 讓"
            },
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "你"
            },
            {
              "chord": "D",
              "text": "愛 流"
            },
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "過， 毫"
            },
            {
              "chord": "A",
              "text": "無"
            },
            {
              "chord": "A7",
              "text": "阻"
            },
            {
              "chord": "D",
              "text": "礙。"
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "1"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "困迫之爱，大能有谁能档？"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "爱潮汹涌，我岂能再顽固？"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "我神，你的恩慈有谁能抗？"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "我今投诚不再依然如故。"
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "2"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "天上之爱攻破我的天然，"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "修直心思、意念所有途径，"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "漫溢我情，纯净所有意愿，"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "使你纯洁生命流通不停。"
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "3"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "如此，我神在我居衷掌权，"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "恩典带爱缓缓涌自心怀；"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "恩爱江河从今流到永远，"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "能爱，是因满享我神大爱。"
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "4"
    }
  ],
